Modes in a Switch/Router:
  1. User EXEC mode (Switch>)
  2. Privileged EXEC mode / Enable mode (Switch#)
  3. Global configuration mode (Switch(config)#)

enable
configure terminal
hostname -------
enable secret ccna
service password-encryption
line console 0
login local
line vty 0 4
login local
exit
username indika secret ccna

In windows,
  arp -d * => clears the arp cache
